{"tid":1897824,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人民日報 : 中国政府和人民抗擊疫情的響噹噹行動，早已在世界範圍贏得廣泛尊重","createTime":"2020-02-26T02:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T10:56:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"86a7dffc86679d6a4c34ff70022a1e16fe567c7b","tid":1897824,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"美國《華爾街日報》不久前發表一篇評論，給文章做了個明顯帶有種族歧視色彩的標題：《中國是真正的「亞洲病夫」》。這樣的文章和標題，不是在描述真相，而是在歪曲事實，暴露的是媒體的傲慢與偏見。應當看到，中國政府和人民抗擊疫情的響噹噹行動，早已在世界範圍贏得廣泛尊重，這是任何中傷、抹黑中國的伎倆都無法改變的事實。阻擊「種族歧視」這個痼疾的發作，也是攜手抗擊疫情的應有之義。 <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200226/34340308.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"34d40653689488e08cac726ce2e65be0695715ad","tid":1897824,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"好叻叻啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場facebook留言：廢除功能組別 投白票都唔投泛民 連登係鬼 泛民賣手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7dcf4fba2632724ee126519ba60e5617418428f8","tid":1897824,"uid":60563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"以為老衲開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4951064ddda9e0a6b0c6ecdab1c667c120ff961","tid":1897824,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d34f59b2e4ba85d6df5d36313ba6cf450721631","tid":1897824,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d402df537eb9a50d8b4b5f45f598ed2eb496d2","tid":1897824,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7dcf4fba2632724ee126519ba60e5617418428f8","tid":1897824,"uid":60563,"lik